title: Study Hall: MAKE A FORTUNE SELLING MERCH
itunes:title: Study Hall: MAKE A FORTUNE SELLING MERCH
description:
In this Study Hall, we sat down with our partner Michael J MacDonald and explained how we tripled our merchandise profit margins in five months. We also detailed the equipment we used, payment systems, supply companies and more. If you’re interested in selling merch, marketing, or e-commerce as a whole.


Link to EYL Merch Store (Black Friday Sale enter Apollo33 for 33% off): https://www.earnyourleisure.com/collections/all


EYL University (70% off Black Friday Sale): https://www.eyluniversity.com
